net.sf.marineapi.nmea.util
Class Time

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.marineapi.nmea.util.Time

public class Time
extends java.lang.Object

Represents a time of day in 24-hour clock, i.e. the UTC time used as default in NMEA 0183. Transmitted by TimeSentence.

Version:
$Revision: 62 $
Author:
Kimmo Tuukkanen
See Also:
TimeSentence, Date
